Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.45,0:19:34.10,SONG-05,,0,0,0,,{\pos(34,42)\3c&H809798&\3a&H35&}不需要那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.58,Caligula,,0,0,0,,μ~~~~~!!!!!!
